fields.name: DataFramed by Data Camp
fields.description: DataFramed is a podcast for data & analytics leaders looking to scale data science throughout their organization by equipping them with the insights to drive value from data science and create a data-driven culture. Each episode will feature a conversation with data science and analytics leaders who are transforming their organizations and are at the forefront of the data revolution.
